name: GotoLastPageBehaviors
shortdesc: A collection of goto last page behavior objects.

method.name: count
method.shortdesc: Displays the number of elements in the GotoLastPageBehavior.

parameters.name: withProperties
parameters.shortdesc: Initial values for properties of the new GotoLastPageBehavior (Optional)

method.name: item
method.shortdesc: Returns the GotoLastPageBehavior with the specified index or name.

parameters.name: index
parameters.shortdesc: The index or name. Can accept: Long Integer or String.

method.name: itemByName
method.shortdesc: Returns the GotoLastPageBehavior with the specified name.

method.name: itemByID
method.shortdesc: Returns the GotoLastPageBehavior with the specified ID.

method.name: itemByRange
method.shortdesc: Returns the GotoLastPageBehaviors within the specified range.

parameters.name: from
parameters.shortdesc: The GotoLastPageBehavior, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: GotoLastPageBehavior, Long Integer or String.

parameters.name: to
parameters.shortdesc: The GotoLastPageBehavior, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: GotoLastPageBehavior, Long Integer or String.

method.name: firstItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the first GotoLastPageBehavior in the collection.

method.name: lastItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the last GotoLastPageBehavior in the collection.

method.name: middleItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the middle GotoLastPageBehavior in the collection.

method.name: previousItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the GotoLastPageBehavior with the index previous to the specified index.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.shortdesc: The index of the GotoLastPageBehavior that follows the desired GotoLastPageBehavior.

method.name: nextItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the GotoLastPageBehavior whose index follows the specified GotoLastPageBehavior in the collection.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.shortdesc: The GotoLastPageBehavior whose index comes before the desired GotoLastPageBehavior.

method.name: anyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns any GotoLastPageBehavior in the collection.

method.name: everyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns every GotoLastPageBehavior in the collection.

method.name: toSource
method.shortdesc: Generates a string which, if executed, will return the GotoLastPageBehavior.
Returns the GotoLastPageBehavior with the specified index.
